	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">TeamworkTechniques</h1>
	<div id="bodyContent">
		<h3 id="siteSub">From SPA Wiki</h3>
		<div id="contentSub">
				<div id="mw-revision-info">Revision as of 12:51, 7 April 2008 by <a href="http://www.spaconference.org/mediawiki/index.php?title=Special:Contributions/CharlesWeir" title="Special:Contributions/CharlesWeir" class="mw-userlink">CharlesWeir</a>  <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="http://www.spaconference.org/mediawiki/index.php?title=User_talk:CharlesWeir&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="User talk:CharlesWeir (page does not exist)">Talk</a>)</span></div>

